OVERVIEW OF THE PROJECT

![Screenshot (5)](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8c1e5608-1425-46fd-955f-841f35e6fe46)



PROJECT: create a program that converts temperatures between Celsius, Fahrenheit, and Kelvin scales.
Objectives
  
  Accurate Conversions:
Ensure precise conversions between Celsius, Fahrenheit, and Kelvin.

  User-Friendly:
Design an intuitive interface for easy temperature input and selection.

  Efficiency:
You can perform quick and efficient conversions for instant results.

Comprehensive:
Support conversions in all directions among the three scales.

Educational Value:
Enhance users' understanding of different temperature scales.
